column54: A notification system would enhance collaboration, I would not have to always monitor the icons (cf Among Us)
Add sound to the indocators, make them blink near a critical threshold, make the panel always facing the camera

I restrained my movements due to the proximity with my collaborator's avatar (even knowing we were physically distant). The panels being face to face, I just had to turn my head which was less demanding than looking at the indicators.
Indicators were useful for the tracking and system monitoring task, less for the communication and resource management tasks.
too many indicators, maybe simplify them or try with fewer
